            "text": "<p>Step into the heart of Canadian craft distilling at our Vernon and Kelowna locations. Guests are invited to<strong>sample our internationally awarded spirits</strong>while discovering the artistry behind our farm-to-flask production. From grain to glass, our team shares the story of how locally grown ingredients are transformed into world-class whisky, gin, vodka, and liqueurs. Whether you’re a curious newcomer or a seasoned enthusiast, each visit offers a<strong>memorable tasting experience</strong>and a deeper appreciation for the craft.</p>",
