            "video_autoplay": false,
            "heading": "Kelowna Distillery",
            "heading_size": "h1",
            "text": "<p>Join us at our Prohibition Edition boutique craft distillery and cocktail lounge in the heart of downtown Kelowna on Bernard Avenue.<br/><br/>With the introduction of prohibition in the 1920s, a shadowy, underground distilling industry sprang into existence. That prohibition spirit is still alive one hundred years later at BC’s Original Craft Distillery. Let our “Prohibition Edition” distillery take you back to where the western frontier’s small-batch farm-to-flask spirit production all began while you savour the spirits that ignited BC’s authentic distilling renaissance.<br/><br/>Our Kelowna distillery was constructed to tread softly on the environment while paying homage to the history of the local fruit industry. You’ll see reclaimed wood from the Laurel and Gellatly Bay fruit packing houses and our recycled spirits glass countertop is sure to catch your eye. The local terroir, our passion, and our family’s Okanagan heritage are expressed throughout our product lineup of whiskies, gins, fruit liqueurs and prebatched premium craft cocktails.</p>",
            "text_style": "body",
            "mobile_text_style": "body--mobile",
